  "original_title": "\u0dab\u0dba \u0dc3\u0dc4\u0db1 \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1 \u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dba  \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dd0\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0da0\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The President asks China to change its stance on debt relief",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe said in a special interview to Nikkei Asia News Service that Sri Lanka is asking China to change its position on debt relief. The President also stated that it will not be easy to reach an agreement in this regard.",
        "Mr. Wickramasinghe said, \"We have informed the Chinese government of the need for debt restructuring and the need to treat all creditors equally.\"",
        "He insists that it will be a complicated path for Beijing to make a difference in this regard, but it will somehow depend on other lenders.",
        "China, Japan and India have given large bilateral loans to Sri Lanka. Sri Lanka's total foreign debt is 51 billion dollars, of which these three countries have 14 billion dollars.",
        "Some independent economists have estimated that the amount of credit given by China to Sri Lanka from 2001 to 2021 is close to 9.95 billion dollars.",
        "Sri Lanka has declared that it is unable to pay the foreign debt of 6.9 billion dollars this year."
      ],
